## Description {#details}

Generic <a href="/docs/api/classes/anonymous-namespace-livedebugvalues-cpp-/livedebugvalues">LiveDebugValues</a> pass.

Calls through to VarLocBasedLDV or <a href="/docs/api/classes/livedebugvalues/instrrefbasedldv">InstrRefBasedLDV</a> to perform location propagation, via the <a href="/docs/api/classes/ldvimpl">LDVImpl</a> base class.
